-Smith-Premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Will-Smith-Premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-smith">威尔·史密斯（Will Smith）2005年的</a>Hit <em>Hitch</em>的导演透露，这位演员试图在制作开始前三天退出电影。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/bad-boys-ride-or-die-review-will-smith-3762339">坏男孩：骑或死评论 - 在方向盘上睡觉</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部浪漫喜剧使这位明星扮演了一位约会专家，他帮助男人吸引了自己梦dream以求的女人，只是让他在自己的浪漫生活中遇到问题。这部电影是一场票房，赚了3.716亿美元，在十年中，史密斯继续成为好莱坞的地位。</p><p> However, to celebrate the movie&#39;s 20th anniversary, director Andy Tennant spoke to <a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/hitch-will-smith-director-behind-the-scenes-interview-2025-1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Business Insider</em></a> about some of the struggles during production.</p><p> “We had our difficulties,” he said of himself and Smith. “我想拍的电影和电影想要制作的电影，这部电影都不像我们一起制作的电影一样好。这是一场战斗。”</p><p> Tennant recalled receiving an unlikely ally in the form of the actor&#39;s wife, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jada-pinkett-smith">Jada Pinkett-Smith</a> .他说：“贾达是一个很大的帮助。” “她有点借调了我的一些直觉。曾经有一段时间在准备中，我回来了很多疯狂的事情。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Hitch (2005) - Trailer" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dMaq_pfxs-0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> This included what Tennant called “crazy story ideas”, saying: “There was a draft that Will brought in that I was not a fan of. I finally told the studio that I was more afraid of Will making that version of the movie than I was about them firing me… to Will&#39;s credit, we didn&#39;t go with that draft. I don&#39;t think I was ever in anyone&#39;s favour.”</p><p> The idea of Smith, best known as an action star, becoming a romantic lead was also met with trepidation.他继续说：“有很多恐惧的恐惧与威尔一起做一部大型，昂贵的浪漫喜剧。” “这充满了危险。威尔在我们开始拍摄之前试图退出三天。 He wanted to shut down and work on it some more.”</p><p> Additionally, Tennant revealed that a sequel was in development – but not with his input. “I guess Will is developing a <em>Hitch</em> sequel without me,” he said.</p><p> “我刚刚在三个月前发现了这件事。我对续集有一个很好的主意，我正在与索尼的一位高管交谈，他说威尔的制作公司正在制作续集。嘿，那是好莱坞。” </p><figure id="attachment_3837300" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837300" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837300" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hitch-Cast-Premiere.jpg" alt="威尔·史密斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hitch-Cast-Premiere.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hitch-Cast-Premiere-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hitch-Cast-Premiere-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hitch-Cast-Premiere-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hitch-Cast-Premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hitch-Cast-Premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837300" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Hitch&#39; cast members Amber Valletta, Will Smith, Kevin James and Eva Mendes promoting the film in 2005. Dave Benett/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Despite clashes on set, the filmmaker didn&#39;t hold any grudges. “I don&#39;t have anything against Will,” he explained. “他雇用我拍这部电影。对于任何人来说，这都不是一件容易的事，但是我们在电影中遍及世界。</p><p> “Even the hard times he&#39;d always say, &#39;Wait until the junket.我们将与这个世界一起走动 - 我们做到了，这很棒。 It was the most amazing trip I had ever been on.”</p><p> However, the pair haven&#39;t spoken since completing the promotion for the movie.他说：“当结束时，我和威尔在一起的时间结束了。” “就是这样。从那以后我再也没有收到他的消息。”</p><p> Recently, Smith made his first appearance at an awards show since his infamous incident at the 2022 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">Oscars</a> when he slapped host <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-rock">Chris Rock</a> . His arrival at this year&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">Grammys</a> was <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/will-smiths-grammys-appearance-goes-down-badly-on-social-media-he-doesnt-deserve-to-be-in-the-spotlight-3834093">not well received by fans online</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-tried-to-pull-out-of-hitch-three-days-before-shooting-claims-director-3837293">Will Smith tried to pull out of &#39;Hitch&#39; “three days before shooting”, claims director</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
